
# **Father's Essays Blog** 📚✍️🎓

This project is dedicated to the dissemination of a collection of essays penned by my wife's father. Initially, there was an aspiration to publish these thought-provoking pieces in a book, but the cost of publication made this option untenable. As an alternative, we decided to create a blog, providing a cost-effective platform for sharing his wisdom. Moreover, this endeavor serves as an avenue for me to hone my web development skills.

The essays cover a myriad of topics and are primarily geared towards the ultra-Orthodox audience. As the project evolves, we plan on incorporating article filters and other features to enrich the user experience.

