## **Installation Instructions** ⚙️ <a name="installation-instructions"></a>

Please follow these step-by-step instructions to get this project up and running on your local machine.

1. Clone the repository 
2. Install all dependencies using npm install
3. To start the server, run the command npm start

_**Note:** More detailed instructions regarding dependencies and their installation will be provided._

## **Usage** 💡 <a name="usage"></a>

### **Registration and Login** 
Upon launching the site, you will be presented with a registration screen. After filling in all necessary details, and validating your email and password, you will then be redirected to the login screen. Once successfully logged in, you will have access to the various essays.

### **Navigating the Blog** 
You will find a broad range of articles to read. To make the navigation easier, we plan to introduce article filters in the future, allowing users to peruse articles based on their preferred categories.

### **Additional Features**
On the side of each article, we've incorporated an element which displays the current time—a small touch to provide added value for our users. 

Users also have the ability to comment on articles, fostering interaction between the author and the readers.

